  {
    "slug": "panton-chair",
    "name": "Panton Chair",
    "brand": "Vitra",
    "category": "furniture",
    "externalUrl": "https://www.vitra.com/en-un/product/panton-chair",
    "availability": "buyable",
    "description": "From boardrooms to dining tables, the Panton chair is a classic.\n\nIt never really worked for the longest time, as the material science was a little behind the vision. The chair famously broke many times before the prototype was ready, but the end result seemed to defy gravity.\n\nThis is one I've sat in many times. The cool plastic and the slight spring make it magic to sit in.\n\nIt instantly brightens up a room, gives it a cool vibe so common in the '60s. This is a piece that, although stylistic, can sit in any situation and own the space.",
    "listingImage": "images/objects/panton-chair-vitra.webp",
    "detailImage": "images/objects/panton-chair-vitra-detail.webp"
  },
